  "title": "Traceability - DOORS Server area Decision",
  "version": 11,
  "url": "/spaces/CARSFW/pages/2491260636/Traceability+-+DOORS+Server+area+Decision",
  "last_modified": "2022-11-08T09:05:22.000+01:00",
  "last_modified_by": "user-1f19a",
  "parent_id": "2410130115",
  "children": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We have three different DOORS area, and we need to decide which one will be suitable for China Convergence Platform and Projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Rng Server → CART",
        "HI Server → China Projects",
        "DOORS Nextgen"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution 1:  CART in Rng and CN PF/Projects in HI server"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Since the CART and China Project DOORS are in different Servers there is a need for DOORS exchange"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For this we need poweruser tool"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Synchronization is done by the Requirements Manager from both sides (CART and BaseSW in our case), exchange frequency will be aligned based on the project needs. Each re-import will be also checked by eXchange for changes which have to be communicated to the teams"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Traceability%20-%20DOORS%20Server%20area%20Decision/image2022-11-7_14-6-29.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Traceability - DOORS Server area Decision/image2022-11-7_14-6-29.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Pros:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "No need to change the China project server"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Cons:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Need High Effort",
        "High complexity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution 2: Both CART and China project DOORS in RNg Server"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Linking can be directly done (No Need for DOORS exchange)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below diagram is from CART RM page - RM Collaboration - CT/ESC Software Home - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Traceability%20-%20DOORS%20Server%20area%20Decision/image2022-11-7_14-10-38.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Traceability - DOORS Server area Decision/image2022-11-7_14-10-38.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Pros:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Less complex",
        "Less effort"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Cons:"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Need to have separate DOORS for SCC and SOC (Since SOC will be in HI Doors)",
        "System and Customer requirements will be available in HI DOORS"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Project team cannot accept"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "panel_type": "info",
      "title": "",
      "content": "CART is having a plan to move to Next gen. At that time both CART and CNCONVPF can move to DOORS next gen"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution 3: CART in Rng and China Convergence in DOORs nextgen"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To be discussed"
    }
  ],
